simplemarkdown (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * PieceTable-based text engine with syntax highlighting
  * Real-time GFM preview powered by cmark-gfm
  * Synchronized scrolling between editor and preview
  * Search and replace functionality
  * Recent files management

